{"name":"Mind Sphere","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You gain the ability to alter the minds of others, causing them to act as you see fit. When you first gain the Mind sphere, you gain the @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.jpbeyOxQ5Tnl2GBn]{charm} ability and one <strong>(charm)</strong> talent of your choice.</p><hr /><p>Some Mind sphere talents are designated <strong>(charm)</strong> talents. These talents grant you charms you can place on targets.</p><p><strong>Charm Talents</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.CdgfQq5VvElUHqcT]{Amnesia (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.1jRUvTuxycCEY77t]{Calm (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.5wYYUvk5rqymArDI]{Candor (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.PYro3p4N7D4MNLGV]{Command (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.XXzoTX0BZ9CMt1ml]{Confusion (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.p5cLMbFybTGORMnt]{Courage (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.mqfVEpnRKdHFywW8]{Disrupt Focus (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.b9xw4bkDSLU3tILu]{Enthrall (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.ibCVp6S26dJv6QdM]{Fear (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.3L5BJm8FtOtU8lVv]{Gestures (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.GwDVvIZuc9ad0ehh]{Hostility (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.83EmNdlZTtIb4FQd]{Inception (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.C2ODPG03g0MSRh3b]{Inspiration (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.NDZZ8advgNzE8Xet]{Mind Shield (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.cOVy7FhxUQQq7IaS]{Mind Spy (charm)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.mind.c8psTzWbse2lrLw5]{Paralyze (charm)}</p></li><li>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-sphere