{"name":"Enhancement Sphere","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can place enhancements on creatures and objects, altering their properties. When you first gain the Enhancement sphere, you gain the @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.ezGOKNckDqrg51UT]{degrade} and @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.bFrhaDngS4YjiQXw]{enhance} abilities and one <strong>(enhance)</strong> or <strong>(degrade)</strong> talent of your choice.</p><p>If an ability grants both @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.ezGOKNckDqrg51UT]{degrade} and @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.bFrhaDngS4YjiQXw]{enhance} options, attempting to apply the @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.ezGOKNckDqrg51UT]{degrade} option to a target under the effects of the @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.bFrhaDngS4YjiQXw]{enhance}, or vice versa, requires you to succeed on a [[/r 1d20 + @mod]]{spellcasting} ability check against the sphere DC of the existing effect; if successful, you counter the previous effect rather than applying the new one.</p><p>Talents marked as <strong>(degrade)</strong> or <strong>(enhance)</strong> grant you new options you can bestow. When using a @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.ezGOKNckDqrg51UT]{degrade} or @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.bFrhaDngS4YjiQXw]{enhance} ability, you choose one option among those you possess to bestow.</p><p>Some talents have a <strong>spell point</strong> cost different than the base @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.ezGOKNckDqrg51UT]{degrade} or @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.bFrhaDngS4YjiQXw]{enhance} abilities; these replace the base cost of the ability when used.</p><hr /><p><strong>Enhance and Degrade Talents</strong></p><ul><li><p>Animate Object (@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.masbkaX4fR54Z8Cz]{degrade}, @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.UnS7D4TpAseB8Gr5]{enhance})</p></li><li><p><span>Bestow Intelligence (@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.iqzkj5DO59gtA0Wc]{degrade}, @UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.u8azRw98aR8u6Ohx]{enhance})</span></p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.xDIiuPVUOJC0r8AU]{Deadly Weapon (degrade, enhance)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.7bNFmUaw8js9UEDQ]{Energy Weapon (enhance)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.0uPW7M6YJrGTO31k]{Enhance Equipment (degrade, enhance)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.8g1i8aXBG8grAihM]{Enhance Poison (degrade, enhance)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.7dEeuHLWTXZzvqGu]{Enhance Size (degrade, enhance)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.nmo6tFkx9cojB7Jv]{False Energy (enhance)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.eaTuzaGNseSZ6TMi]{Manipulate Hardness (degrade, enhance)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.2w8v6aC1lDfAcLrp]{Mental Enhancement (degrade, enhance)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.dshQuBL5ob1gKJQp]{Muffle Sound (degrade, enhance)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.SfPL4Eym8sB1on1s]{Physical Enhancement (degrade, enhance)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.2iRHJwoyYaTVgttn]{Speed Control (degrade, enhance)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.eH4ZfLxzviHinVrY]{Staunch Resistance (degrade, enhance)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.hxcz0iiB4a3zpBmY]{Steal Ability (degrade)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.fW8YGJbasQjvcXAp]{Weight Control (degrade, enhance)}</p></li></ul><hr /><p><strong>Other Talents</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.enhancement.uvhtVZVHwzfCUCJ2]{Dual Enhancement}</p></li></ul><hr /><p><strong>Advanced Talents</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.wolfer-spheres5e.